<title>登陆失败</title>
</head>
<body>
	<p>登陆失败</p><br>
	<p style="color: blue"><span id=jump>3</span> 秒钟后页面将返回登陆页面...</p>
<script>
	function countDown(secs) {
		jump.innerText = secs;
		if (--secs > 0)
			setTimeout("countDown(" + secs + " )", 1000);
	}
	countDown(3);
</script>

</body>
</html>